<paragraph id="1A2DFB1DF031884162BF3CC8584CFE53" blockId="12.[143,794,241,425]" pageId="12" pageNumber="181">
Comentários. Amorfologia geral do macho de 
<taxonomicName id="DD92809EF031884160F13CCB585CFED3" authorityName="Piran" authorityYear="1959" class="Insecta" family="Pentatomidae" genus="Mecocephala" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="181" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="curculionoides">
<emphasis id="28E6270FF031884160F13CCB585CFED3" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="181">M. curculionoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
é semelhante à da fêmea de 
<taxonomicName id="DD92809EF031884160523D2B5BC9FED3" authority="Schwertner &amp; Grazia &amp; Fernandes, 2002" authorityName="Schwertner &amp; Grazia &amp; Fernandes" authorityYear="2002" box="[600,699,273,297]" class="Insecta" family="Pentatomidae" genus="Mecocephala" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="181" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zikani" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="28E6270FF031884160523D2B5BC9FED3" box="[600,699,273,297]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="181">M. zikani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="28E6270FF031884160CA3D285A63FED3" bold="true" box="[704,785,273,297]" pageId="12" pageNumber="181">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="33D59A74F031884160CA3D285A63FED3" box="[704,785,273,297]" pageId="12" pageNumber="181" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, diferindo desta por ser de menor tamanho, a coloração do corpo variando de castanho-escura a castanho-clara, comas margens ântero-laterais do pronoto, base do hemiélitro e pernas, castanho-claras.
</paragraph>
